Name: ZombieMaze
About the game: About this game 'Helicopter is on the roof!!!' You are the brave person who can survive zombie appocalipes. there are 3 types of the zombie!! run!! 'Zombie maze' is simply hard game with zombie shooting game. Player have to find the way to go upstair with killing the zombies. You don't have to kill all the zombies on the floor but you better kill all the zombies. Can you make it to the roof? 'Zombie Maze' features 12 floors with zombies. all different map with tons of zombies. Disclaimer JO is not responsible for nightmares or dizziness. Controls Move with WASD keys relaod gun with R key change weapon with TAB menu for ESC and the finally you can kill zombie with MOUSE LEFT click Requirements 'Zombie Maze' can work on any Windows computer.
